            "answer_text": "No smartphones actually provide any special eye protection feature. If you want to protect your eye then you shouldn't use your phone in high brightness, keep it in auto brightness and in night time usage use can use blue light filter apps. And finally don't get addicted to phone instead have a descent usage. Also maintain a distance from the screen. ",
